===Overview===
The '''Tandar-Kaan''' are a tribe of primitive [[humans]] that live in the [[Savage Land]]. They are expert ship builders and fishermen. The Tandar-Kaan form a community of multiple barges on the river Tabar, allowing them to move to new shores whenever they want. They moved their after a large number of the population was killed during a earthquake.{{r|Ka-Zar Vol 2 6}}
